iment zone.\",\n      href: \"/platforms/garage\",\n      color: \"border-[#00FF9D]/20 hover:border-[#00FF9D]/50 hover:bg-[#00FF9D]/5\",\n      badge: \"Innovation\",\n    }\n  ];\n\n  const gridPlatforms = [\n    {\n      title: \"Garage Innovation Suite\",\n      category: \"Innovation Layer\",\n      href: \"/platforms/garage\",\n      desc: \"Collaborative portal for executive framing, architectural design workshops, and secure rapid-prototyping sandbox environments.\",\n      features: [\"Strategic Discovery\", \"Architecture Workshops\", \"Prototyping Labs\", \"Experiment Zone Playground\"],\n      themeColor: \"#00FF9D\",\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Foundry Visual Studio\",\n      category: \"Co-creation Layer\",\n      href: \"/platforms/foundry\",\n      desc: \"Our professional IDE to build systems. Manage relational database fabric ingest and configure cognitive core supervisors.\",\n      features: [\"Visual Flow Canvas\", \"Secure Local Runtime\", \"Dynamic Data Fabric\", \"Enterprise AI Engineering\"],\n      themeColor: \"#009DFF\",\n    },\n    {\n      title: \"Factory Scaling Portal\",\n      category: \"Industrialisation Layer\",\n      href: \"/platforms/factory\",\n      desc: \"The operations control tower. Manage security guardrail policies, horizontal clustering, and cost tracking logs.\",\n      features: [\"Horizontal Clustering\", \"Observability Dashboard\", \"Human Audit Gates\", \"Cost Attribution Logs\"],\n      themeColor: \"#FF3B30\",\n    }\n  ];\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Productized Assets\"\n        title=\"Enterprise Platforms\"\n        highlightedWord=\"Platforms\"\n        description=\"Transform enterprise operations with GFF AI's suite of secure sovereign software platforms. Build, audit, and run multi-agent cognitive systems with total control.\"\n      />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-24\">\n        \n        {/* SECTION 1