{"ts":"2026-06-26T01:15:05.478Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Designing the Factory Page**\n\nI'm now focused on the `/platforms/factory/page.tsx` file, envisioning it as the Industrialisation Layer. My key requirements for this design are: the inclusion of Scale, Monitor, and Operate functionalities. I'm structuring these features, aiming to represent these key concepts, within the factory page.\n\n\n**Drafting the Premium Design**\n\nI'm currently drafting a premium design for the `/platforms/factory/page.tsx` file. I've fleshed out the hero section, including the \"INDUSTRIALISATION LAYER\" category, \"GFF AI Factory\" title, with \"Factory\" highlighted, and a description. I'm also working on a narrative section that describes the industrialization layer, highlighting GFF AI Factory's role as a Tier 3 solution. I'm focusing on features such as horizontal auto-scaling and an interactive \"Observability Monitor Dashboard\".\n\n\n**Defining Operational Aspects**\n\nI am now focusing on operational aspects like life-cycle management, approval workflows, and memory state backups. I'm also considering monetization, specifically pricing logs, usage metrics, and value audits. My goal is to write a clean, concise `app/platforms/factory/page.tsx` file using the editor tool, aiming for under 3000 characters to ensure it's deployable.\n\n\n**Analyzing Performance Metrics**\n\nI'm now diving into performance metrics. I've integrated a `useEffect` hook to simulate throughput and latency fluctuations. I'm dynamically updating the values with a `setInterval` that runs every 2 seconds, which will provide a realistic impression. I'm using `Math.random()` to generate randomized changes within a defined range, ensuring realistic variability. I'm focusing on ensuring these metrics reflect a real-world scenario.\n\n\n**Visualizing the Functionality**\n\nI'm now visualizing the functionality as the mission-critical control tower in Tier 3 of the GFF Operating Model. I'm focusing on its auto-scaling operations, SLA monitoring, and the human-approval loops. I'm also considering the dashboard showing cluster throughput as a key performance indicator. This will inform the detailed design.\n\n\n**Refining Display Metrics**\n\nI'm now refining the display metrics within the UI. I'm focusing on the presentation of throughput, latency, and safety policy status. I am working on the throughput metric, represented in t/sec, as well as median latency in ms, and a safety policy with memory locks. I aim to improve the visual clarity and impact of these key indicators for the user.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T01:15:05.491Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"yixrbt3a","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/platforms/factory/page.tsx","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport InnerPageShell from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageShell\";\nimport InnerPageHero from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageHero\";\nimport MotionReveal from \"@/components/inner-pages/MotionReveal\";\nimport PremiumCTA from \"@/components/inner-pages/PremiumCTA\";\n\nexport default function FactoryPage() {\n  const [throughput, setThroughput] = useState(412);\n  const [latency, setLatency] = useState(118);\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const interval = setInterval(() => {\n      setThroughput((prev) => Math.min(600, Math.max(300, prev + Math.floor(Math.random() * 21) - 10)));\n      setLatency((prev) => Math.min(180, Math.max(90, prev + Math.floor(Math.random() * 9) - 4)));\n    }, 2000);\n    return () => clearInterval(interval);\n  }, []);\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Industrialisation Layer\"\n        title=\"GFF AI Factory\"\n        highlightedWord=\"Factory\"\n        description=\"Scale, monitor, operate, and monetize sovereign agent networks at global scale.\"\n      />\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-16\">\n        <MotionReveal className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center py-10 border-y border-white/5\">\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-5\">\n            <span className=\"text-xs font-mono text-[#FF3B30] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold\">Enterprise Operations</span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-2\">The Industrialisation Layer</h2>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"lg:col-span-7\">\n            <p className=\"text-white/70 font-light text-sm\">\n              The Factory is Tier 3 of GFF's Operating Model. It is the mission-critical control tower that handles auto-scaling operations, monitors SLA requirements, executes human-approval loops, and attributes usage costs across business units.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        <MotionReveal className=\"space-y-6\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center\">Observability Monitor</h2>\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n            <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n              <span className=\"text-xs font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">Cluster Throughput</span>\n              <span className=\"text-3xl font-mono font-bold text-[#FF3B30] mt-3\">{throughput} t/sec</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 mt-1 uppercase\">Active horizontal nodes</span>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n              <span className=\"text-xs font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">Median Latency</span>\n              <span className=\"text-3xl font-mono font-bold text-[#FF3B30] mt-3\">{latency} ms</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 mt-1 uppercase\">Sovereign routing overhead</span>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n              <span className=\"text-xs font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">Safety Policy Status</span>\n              <span className=\"text-3xl font-mono font-bold text-green-500 mt-3\">100% SECURE</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 mt-1 uppercase\">Memory lock active</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        <MotionReveal className=\"space-y-6\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center\">Factory Core Modules</h2>\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\">\n            {[\n              { title: \"Scale\", desc: \"Horizontal auto-scaling agent clustering with isolated CPU and memory groups.\" },\n              { title: \"Monitor\", desc: \"Real-time SLA telemetry, active compliance auditing, and threat logs.\" },\n              { title: \"Operate\", desc: \"Backup states, Human-in-the-Loop manager approval gates, and hot-updates.\" },\n              { title: \"Monetize\", desc: \"Multi-tenant cost attribution logs, token volume logs, and attribution metrics.\" }\n            ].map((m) => (\n              <div key={m.title} className=\"p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-[#FF3B30]/20 transition-all\">\n                <h3 className=\"font-bold text-white text-sm mb-2\">{m.title}</h3>\n                <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-light\">{m.desc}</p>\n              </div>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n        </MotionReveal>\n\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Architect Your Sovereign Operation\"\n          description=\"Schedule a technical consultation to scope, design, and deploy private agent grids with GFF engineers.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Contact Systems Engineers\"\n          primaryHref=\"/contact\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}"}}}
